additionalProperty.value: Diamond flammable symbol . Extremely Flammable box logo ANZ AEROSOL WARNING STATEMENT WARNING: DO NOT SPRAY NEAR A NAKED FLAME OR ANY HOT SURFACE. KEEP AWAY FROM SOURCES OF IGNITION - NO SMOKING. AVOID DIRECT INHALATION. USE IN WELL VENTILATED PLACES, AVOID PROLONGED SPRAYING. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.. Dove and Dove Men+Care Aerosol Safety Caution CAUTION: Pressurised dispenser. Protect from sunlight and do not expose to temperatures exceeding 50C. Do not pierce or burn, even when empty. Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents may be harmful or fatal..
